<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta http-equiv=3D"Content-Type" content=3D"tex=
t/html; charset=3DUTF-8"><link rel=3D"stylesheet" type=3D"text/css" href=3D=
"cid:css-d2fe008f-a72b-4cd2-b952-6790d0dbff2f@mhtml.blink" />
    <title>GenMatDesign-AI</title>
    <meta name=3D"viewport" content=3D"width=3Ddevice-width, initial-scale=
=3D1">
   =20
</head>
<body>
<div class=3D"container">
    <div class=3D"hero">
        <h1>GenMatDesign-AI</h1>
        <p>Generative AI for inverse materials design of solid-state batter=
y electrolytes using a Conditional VAE, surrogate modeling, uncertainty est=
imation, and deployable Flask APIs.</p>
    </div>

    <div class=3D"status">
        <b>Device:</b> cpu |
        <b>Models Ready:</b> True |
        <b>Internal Library Size:</b> 35
    </div>

    <div class=3D"grid">
        <div class=3D"card">
            <h2>1. Train Internal Model</h2>
            <p class=3D"muted">Train the generator and surrogate model usin=
g the built-in electrolyte library.</p>
            <form method=3D"post" action=3D"http://127.0.0.1:5045/web/train=
">
                <button type=3D"submit">Train Model</button>
            </form>
           =20
           =20
        </div>

        <div class=3D"card">
            <h2>2. Predict One Electrolyte</h2>
            <p class=3D"muted">Enter an electrolyte sequence such as <code>=
PEO-LiTFSI-SN-Al2O3</code>.</p>
            <form method=3D"post" action=3D"http://127.0.0.1:5045/web/predi=
ct">
                <input type=3D"text" name=3D"sequence" value=3D"PEO-LiTFSI-=
SN-Al2O3">
                <button type=3D"submit">Predict Properties</button>
            </form>
           =20
           =20
           =20
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class=3D"card" style=3D"margin-top:18px;">
        <h2>3. Inverse Design from Desired Properties</h2>
        <p class=3D"muted">Specify target properties and generate new candi=
date electrolyte sequences ranked by closeness to target.</p>
        <form method=3D"post" action=3D"http://127.0.0.1:5045/web/generate"=
>
            <div class=3D"grid">
                <div>
                    <label>Ionic Conductivity</label>
                    <input type=3D"text" name=3D"ionic_conductivity" value=
=3D"1.75">
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label>Stability Window</label>
                    <input type=3D"text" name=3D"stability_window" value=3D=
"5.15">
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label>Glass Transition Temp</label>
                    <input type=3D"text" name=3D"glass_transition_temp" val=
ue=3D"29">
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label>Stability Score</label>
                    <input type=3D"text" name=3D"stability_score" value=3D"=
0.90">
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label>Top K</label>
                    <input type=3D"text" name=3D"top_k" value=3D"10">
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label>Export</label>
                    <button formaction=3D"http://127.0.0.1:5045/web/export"=
 formmethod=3D"get" type=3D"submit">Download Last Generated CSV</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button type=3D"submit">Generate Candidates</button>
        </form>

       =20
    </div>

    <div class=3D"grid" style=3D"margin-top:18px;">
        <div class=3D"card">
            <h2>4. Architecture</h2>
            <div class=3D"mono">Built-in Electrolyte Library
        =E2=86=93
Tokenization + Vocabulary
        =E2=86=93
Conditional VAE Generator
        =E2=86=93
Surrogate Property Predictor
        =E2=86=93
Inverse Design from Target Properties
        =E2=86=93
Candidate Ranking + Uncertainty
        =E2=86=93
Dashboard + REST API</div>
        </div>

        <div class=3D"card">
            <h2>5. API</h2>
            <div class=3D"mono">GET  /api
GET  /health
POST /train
POST /predict
POST /generate
GET  /export</div>

            <h3>Example /predict payload</h3>
            <div class=3D"mono">{
  "sequence": "PEO-LiTFSI-SN-Al2O3"
}</div>

            <h3>Example /generate payload</h3>
            <div class=3D"mono">{
  "target": {
    "ionic_conductivity": 1.75,
    "stability_window": 5.15,
    "glass_transition_temp": 29.0,
    "stability_score": 0.90
  },
  "top_k": 10
}</div>
        </div>
    </div>

   =20

    <div class=3D"footer-note">
        This repository is a portfolio-grade inverse materials design proto=
type for GitHub. The internal library is illustrative and intended for demo=
nstration, not publication-grade discovery.
    </div>
</div>

</body></html>
